      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADA BLAZE (1) flew the lids with a fast early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (17.46) over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Has ability and can bounce back. TENACIOUS DESIGN (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish half a length away in second (19.79) behind Hayden's Milk at Angle Park. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can feature again. CATCH MY DESIGN (8) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (16.99) in a Grade 6 at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. QUEEN OF SLAY (4) returns from a five-and-a-half weeks layoff and must be included.",
